org.rhwlab.snight
Class Loc

java.lang.Object
  org.rhwlab.snight.Loc
public class Loc
extends java.lang.Object

Loc is used in Identity and Analysis4. It converts the y and z coordinates of the embryo to ADL orientation. If the embryo orientation is ADL nothing changes. If it is AVR then the values are converted. This is necessary for applying the NEWCANONICAL naming rules. The converted values are available as public members of Loc.

Version:
1.0
Author:
biowolp
